EFF, others? Are you aware Disconnect has changed their configuration to be a Actual VPN on iOS and no longer as Virtual VPN making AVG VPN and other actual VPNs fail to work alongside? Disconnect is now in need of competition bc their star rating down to 3.1. Here’s the thing: as long as you have your iPhone backed up, and can configure your new iPhone from that backup -> you are grandfathered in. If not  This is the second time this has happened. The first I thot a fluke bc pet improvement per iOS Senior Dev.  This I did not anticipate and I did have back ups but if cc prob and a late pay Apple delete delete delete all over 50gb 
If their is an equal to Disconnect let me know
